Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of my dad's job, my mom and sisters moved overseas,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so starting this spring, I started living alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,However, my first time living alone lasted only a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rikka. I'm opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, already. We start school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I attempted to keep my dark chuunibyou history hidden,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and start life over again in high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,just like I did last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi Rikka here foiled me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I command you to awaken, Takanashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tyrant's Eye! The time of awakening has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikka, is sunny side up okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dark side up," please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sunny side up" it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave her too many options.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the ribbon for my uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Was it them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I told you to prepare it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a busy time! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll yank out your stupid cowlick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! It's my "charm point"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This spring, Rikka's mother also had to move out of town for work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...which meant Rikka had to live on her own too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:22.59,OS,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho, heave-ho, heave-ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Rikka's baggage being moved out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Have they finally made their move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Her grandfather accidentally terminated the contract on their apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is sabotage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you'll have to move in with me until you've settled on a new place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency Code: Triple Four activating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, Rikka came to live with me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to be woken up by you, Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,See it from my point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.93,OS,,0,0,0,,The Priestess wouldn't be okay with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I lied to Touka-san and told her I found Rikka an apartment for her alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've been keeping up this facade for about a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Chimera, I give you my demonic fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting used to these red fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This proves nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give it a little try. They're as good as strawberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're becoming more and more like the Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you under her influence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Yuuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.98,OS,,0,0,0,,The fluid! The green gooey stuff is attacking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:32.08,OS,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait! Stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.25,OS,,0,0,0,,Wiping it will just make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:37.22,OS,,0,0,0,,You need to dab it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:43.34,OS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you're heading out, please bring a collapsible umbrella with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:46.52,OS,,0,0,0,,You could say we're going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:48.35,OS,,0,0,0,,We're going out, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:52.35,OS,,0,0,0,,How do you even have romance if it has to be hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never even had a normal girlfriend before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so a chuunibyou girlfriend will be more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Things worked out not to be too different than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guten morgen{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nibutani Shinka, and I'm starting my second year today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibutani-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibutani-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it another good year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,High school second-year syndrome?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to say this one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better remember what we talked about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on the hieroglyphs, the magic barrier attack
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,triggered by the Freemasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe our uninvited guests from the inscrutable parallel world?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wrong too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean performing Schrödinger's cat experiment using Chimera?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Never! We won't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know. About how we're living together at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now, that's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the only thing we talked about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We should visit the real estate agent again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are referring to my new base, it has already been located.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the demon world of the impossibly Wicked One,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,invisible to mere mortals!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were being serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll yank out your stupid cowlick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Flirting this early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Isshiki. Isshiki Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me! The guy in the Light Music Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy who sacrificed everything for Kumi-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the crew cut guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Crew Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me Crew Cut! That version of me is no longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at my Rock'n'Roll hairdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isshiki, what happened to your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go visit the student councilor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My hair type changed when it grew back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kumin-senpai! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who that was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikka-chan! Togashi-kun! Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both second-years starting today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're a third-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. And it's  so much responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, because of studying for university.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh, that isn't what I mean. I'm disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because high school third year is a "turd" year!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it told me to deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know? I want to make everyone laugh just like how Morisummer-chan did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Growing older brings many changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Morisummer-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning! What's up with your outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do, Kumin-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I am wearing normal attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"How do you do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you maybe have early-onset dementia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, if I might have a word...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Morisummer-chan, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, let's make this another spirited school year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a lot of mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but my second year will be completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I will claw my way to the top of this school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}The next speech comes from our new students...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}represented by Dekomori Sanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}I am the new student representative, Dekomori Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}With the warm days of Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}the trees become enrobed in fresh, new green livery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that she got better grades than you had last year, Nibutani-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Our student lives also begin anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just {\i1}great{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Deko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe everyone knows that there are both white and black worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Seeing spirits requires the proper heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"Love is everything."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, Nibutani-san has fainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing, those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same class again, Light Being.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Takanashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same class!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have another good year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanase-sensei is our home room teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:21.33,OS,,0,0,0,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They told me to get my hair cut by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'd know? This is your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are we in the same class again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm in Class 3 next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that relief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even try to hide your relief at {\i1}all{\i0} !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Togashi-kun, a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Togashi's friend? I'm Nibutani—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Pot, meet kettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only bringing this up because we're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Tatenashi-san not to mention our middle school matters {\i1}at all{\i0}, period.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still going on about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I considered it all summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,About whether I'd be going to this high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I really intend to spend three years of my life in that loser's club—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Servant to the Tyrant's Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mjolnir Hammer, Dekomori Sanae...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...is hereby reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the deviously devious Fake Morisummer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,would dare attack Dekomori in her temporary guise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your very nature disgusts me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I spin right-to-left, and left-to-right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposing revolutions shall produce a kink between dimensions and space!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And by adding an additional revolution, I shall produce unlimited power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! The Mjolnir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure have weak semicircular canals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dekomori will not be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're such an energetic first-year...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,as a reward, I will give you the cheese you love. So. Much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you're overdoing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One must take responsibility for one's creations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Paging a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi-san from Year 2, Class 4. Takanashi Rikka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please report to the staff room immediately. I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi-san from Year 2, Class 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,please report to the staff room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The school has been overrun by terrorists!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No it hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm. The school mailed at least three to your home, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all returned to sender.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps because my existence had been erased from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When we phone you, it says that number is not in use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My existence had been erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But you exist right now, so perhaps it'll go through now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My eye! My eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not going to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She seemed to buy it, but at this rate, it'll get ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just try to take a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikka, would you like to come sit with us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The incubus lives in that coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I, who was forged in darkness, dare not approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I once experienced a frightening dream while under its influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What was the dream about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, the light! The Light Being is paralyzing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did that sound questioning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No particular reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In what place would you choose to reside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Reside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What we were talking just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding your base and battle formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For the base, which the Tyrant's Eye and the Dark Flame Master demand,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,will be the base where the magical magnetic field is also the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:12:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibutani.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's with that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that idiot here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what she did to my costume for Theatre Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sleeping inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that's convenient...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to search for a new base.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Base?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea where you should find your own 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I desire a underground labyrinth. But an ancient castle is also okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Opposite the convenience store, there's a castle with "British Parliament" on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! You definitely can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I didn't realize how expensive rent is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I knew it might be expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't know much about it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If I transfer to a new base, will I not be able to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I go to and from school, I won't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it'll probably be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to go to your room to report activity in the magical realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be good if you don't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drop by to pick you up for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's search for a place that we can play at and is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to stay together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibutani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi-san's apartment is empty. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you move, Rikka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I have an explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Touka...-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving for Italy soon, but you won't give me your new home's address. Nor answer your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that's not it, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You remain unwilling to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dekomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right to chase Fake Summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Your servant Dekomori will buy you time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Masters, please evacuate to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize who you're up against?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the priestess who, in a previous battle once force-fed Dekomori a mass of rotten dairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no worthier opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Your hand! Your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know what you guys intend to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're wrong! This is...this is Fake Morisummer's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?! This was your fault to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dekomori deeply respects you, Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As my master's sister, I am at your command!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop trying to throw me under the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are such good friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. My hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, prepare for combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Assume positions and prepare to intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Be destroyed, real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Burst open, synapses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanishment this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Matter Blaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She easily deflected master's Dark Matter Blaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of person is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all or nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,L!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,LO!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,LOV!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,LOVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a physical attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Direct Impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Machine Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Schwarz Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrostire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's arrostire?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It means "oven roasted."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're living together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, it's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're living together as boyfriend and girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please control your disgusting imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, disgusting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're the one with the dirty mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:35.42,OS,,0,0,0,,W-what? I, Dekomori, am always pure of thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.00,OS,,0,0,0,,You're totally red!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.90,OS,,0,0,0,,For a little kid, you have a really dirty mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:43.62,OS,,0,0,0,,Be quiet! Be quiet, you big-boobed freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:44.18,OS,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:47.06,OS,,0,0,0,,Shacking is sooo shocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:49.57,OS,,0,0,0,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:53.97,OS,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's really not what you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.46,OS,,0,0,0,,...and we had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:58.10,OS,,0,0,0,,You're saying that a high school boy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:00.18,OS,,0,0,0,,and my little sister, who are in a romantic relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,had no choice but to move in together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No th-that's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not in a romantic relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys broke up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You dissolved your pact?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who dumped whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.07,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it! I'm saying we didn't "move in together"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that different?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are living together...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because I was worried about leaving Rikka on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been almost a week now, and nothing of that sort is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Of what sort?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Our contract remains unaltered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, we didn't "move in together"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! It's home share!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a home share situation. You know—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that logic will work on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I will permit that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, you can't live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I will find her an apartment. If you have a problem with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...I will take Rikka to Italy with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Italy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The magical society! The Cardinal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I to be imprisoned in such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Italy is home to the occult!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Vatican, Sixth Sense, I see dead people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Home to the occult?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you want to go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuzuha, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear I was coming back for the new school term?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Heard? From whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,From Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been living together with Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, she doesn't have a home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We have plenty of rooms here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I felt uneasy about Rikka living alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you little sister supervises, it should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Please let her stay here just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and find your own place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, my life alone with Rikka came to an abrupt end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and three teenagers began life together in spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta's notebook. I forgot to return it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What the-?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone new move in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She never was able to get her apartment back.
